{
  "info": {
    "name": "EcoMarket API",
    "description": "Colección de endpoints del backend de EcoMarket — Trabajo Práctico Integrador, Taller de Construcción de Software (INF243), UES21 2026.\n\n## Cómo usar\n\n1. Levantar el backend (por defecto en http://localhost:8080).\n2. Las requests usan la variable {{baseUrl}} — viene configurada como http://localhost:8080.\n3. Orden sugerido para probar el flujo completo:\n   - Listar productos\n   - Crear carrito\n   - Agregar items al carrito\n   - Ver carrito\n   - Confirmar orden\n   - Ver historial de órdenes\n\nLa request \"Crear carrito\" guarda automáticamente el id en la variable {{carritoId}} usando un script de tests.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "ecomarket-api-collection-2026"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "carritoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "itemId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "productoId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "ordenId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Productos",
      "description": "CRUD del catálogo de productos.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar productos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/productos",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "productos"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve todos los productos activos del catálogo."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener producto por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/productos/{{productoId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "productos", "{{productoId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Termo de bambú 500ml\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Termo ecológico con mango de bambú y interior de acero.\",\n  \"precio\": 7500.00,\n  \"stock\": 40,\n  \"categoria\": \"Hogar\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/productos",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "productos"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo producto. Devuelve 201 Created."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Cepillo de bambú XL\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Versión más grande del cepillo biodegradable.\",\n  \"precio\": 1800.00,\n  \"stock\": 150,\n  \"categoria\": \"Higiene\",\n  \"activo\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/productos/{{productoId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "productos", "{{productoId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar producto (soft delete)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/productos/{{productoId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "productos", "{{productoId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Marca el producto como inactivo. Devuelve 204 No Content."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Carrito",
      "description": "Gestión del carrito de compras.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear carrito",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('carritoId', json.id);",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "pm.test('Devuelve id', function () { pm.expect(json.id).to.be.a('number'); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/carritos",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "carritos"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo carrito vacío. El id devuelto se guarda en la variable {{carritoId}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Ver carrito",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/carritos/{{carritoId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "carritos", "{{carritoId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve los ítems del carrito + total calculado."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Agregar item al carrito",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.items && json.items.length > 0) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('itemId', json.items[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productoId\": 1,\n  \"cantidad\": 2\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/carritos/{{carritoId}}/items",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "carritos", "{{carritoId}}", "items"]
            },
            "description": "Agrega un producto al carrito. Si el producto ya estaba, suma la cantidad. El id del item se guarda en {{itemId}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Modificar cantidad de item",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cantidad\": 5\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/carritos/{{carritoId}}/items/{{itemId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "carritos", "{{carritoId}}", "items", "{{itemId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar item del carrito",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/carritos/{{carritoId}}/items/{{itemId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "carritos", "{{carritoId}}", "items", "{{itemId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Órdenes",
      "description": "Confirmación de pedidos e historial.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Confirmar orden",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('ordenId', json.id);",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "pm.test('Tiene total > 0', function () { pm.expect(Number(json.total)).to.be.above(0); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"carritoId\": {{carritoId}},\n  \"mensaje\": \"Por favor entregar después de las 18hs. ¡Gracias!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ordenes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "ordenes"]
            },
            "description": "Confirma el carrito como una orden. Descuenta stock y marca el carrito como confirmado."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Historial de órdenes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ordenes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "ordenes"]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve todas las órdenes, más recientes primero."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener orden por id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ordenes/{{ordenId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "ordenes", "{{ordenId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
